      <title>议员称格陵兰独立公投还需数年时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/greenland-s-independence-referendum-is-years-away-lawmaker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦议会一位资深议员表示，随着唐纳德·特朗普重新对格陵兰岛产生兴趣，格陵兰岛成为地缘政治关注的焦点，但该国可能仍需要几年时间来安排独立公投。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/greenland-s-independence-referendum-is-years-away-lawmaker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 17:19:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩尔多瓦与欧盟就应对能源危机采取紧急措施达成一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/moldova-eu-agree-on-emergency-steps-to-tackle-energy-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦和欧盟制定了一项紧急计划，以帮助因俄罗斯天然气供应中断而陷入能源危机的亲俄分离地区德涅斯特河沿岸地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/moldova-eu-agree-on-emergency-steps-to-tackle-energy-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 17:04:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼称若美国发动贸易战，加拿大可利用电力作为筹码</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/carney-says-canada-can-use-electricity-for-leverage-if-us-starts-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正在竞选加拿大总理的前央行行长马克·卡尼表示，如果加拿大政府需要对特朗普政府的关税进行报复，那么它应该愿意限制对美国的电力出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/carney-says-canada-can-use-electricity-for-leverage-if-us-starts-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 17:01:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格塞斯誓言五角大楼将全力支持特朗普的大规模驱逐行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/hegseth-vows-pentagon-is-all-in-on-trump-s-mass-deportation-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长皮特·赫格塞斯周一抵达五角大楼，誓言支持唐纳德·特朗普总统的大规模驱逐行动，并表示军事介入“是国防部绝对会继续做的事情”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/hegseth-vows-pentagon-is-all-in-on-trump-s-mass-deportation-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 16:59:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰国防采购冲突可能影响武器交付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/ukraine-defense-procurement-conflict-may-hit-weapon-deliveries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰国防部长因解雇负责武器供应的重要官员而面临越来越多的批评，在乌克兰军队努力阻止俄罗斯进攻之际，这可能会使其与外国伙伴发生裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/ukraine-defense-procurement-conflict-may-hit-weapon-deliveries</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 16:44:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数千名巴勒斯坦人返回北加沙被毁的家园</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/thousands-of-palestinians-return-to-northern-gaza-as-ceasefire-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着脆弱的 42 天停火协议进入第二周，数万名在以色列与哈马斯战争中流离失所的巴勒斯坦人正在返回加沙北部遭到严重破坏的社区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/thousands-of-palestinians-return-to-northern-gaza-as-ceasefire-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 11:50:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将于下月恢复监控加沙拉法口岸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/eu-looks-to-resume-monitoring-gaza-s-rafah-crossing-on-feb-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟最高外交官卡贾·卡拉斯周一表示，欧盟同意重新启动在加沙和埃及之间拉法口岸的边境援助任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/eu-looks-to-resume-monitoring-gaza-s-rafah-crossing-on-feb-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 09:02:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利退缩 欧盟同意延长对俄罗斯制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/eu-set-to-agree-to-extend-russia-sanctions-hungary-to-back-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在匈牙利放弃反对后，欧盟各国外交部长周一同意延长对俄罗斯的制裁，以抗议俄罗斯与乌克兰的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/eu-set-to-agree-to-extend-russia-sanctions-hungary-to-back-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 07:04:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普暂缓对哥伦比亚征收 25% 关税，就移民问题达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/us-to-hold-off-on-colombia-tariffs-white-house-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布对哥伦比亚征收全面关税，但在就遣返被驱逐移民达成协议后，他突然撤回威胁，此举在数小时内震惊了全球市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/us-to-hold-off-on-colombia-tariffs-white-house-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 03:20:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
