      <title>逮捕令、运气：特朗普驱逐出境突袭行动内部情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-27/arrest-warrants-luck-inside-a-trump-deportation-raid-at-dawn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，移民大扫荡针对了芝加哥数百人，多个机构参与其中，菲尔博士还进行了现场直播。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-27/arrest-warrants-luck-inside-a-trump-deportation-raid-at-dawn</guid>
